original_title: Stevie Ray Vaughan South Texas Tornado Jam
overview: Decent quality Pro-shot Broadcast recordings of Stevie Ray Vaughan, recorded live at Steve Ely’s South Texas Tornado Jam, in Manor Downs, TX on July 11th, 1981.  DVD has a total running time of 29 minutes, and quality is about 7/10.  Tracks are as follows:  Come on Look at little sister Dirty pool Love struck baby You’ll be mine Manic depression
title: Stevie Ray Vaughan South Texas Tornado Jam
